## Future Vision

The Outside Inn is designed to become more than one person's stream. Eventually, the 24/7 channel could host other creators—guest streamers who fit the vibe, taking scheduled slots at the Inn while the radio plays behind them. Programming blocks. Partnerships. A media destination, not just a lofi stream.

E.I. Werner will always be the founder and flagship host. But the Inn is bigger than one innkeeper.

That's Year 2. For now: build the foundation, grow the audience, prove the model.

